{"tid":1289841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[好人好事]好想多謝頭先喺香港大學站恆生ATM拎返錢俾我嗰位巴打","createTime":"2019-07-06T09:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T09:29:45.000Z","uid":137628,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbfe580792dfb828d85179657e45200d09d0dfd","tid":1289841,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:22:10.000Z","msg":"今日大概16:40左右我喺香港大學站恆生撳錢，我嗰下望住自己個餘額發吽逗。當時我聽緊歌其他咩都聽唔到，拎返自己張咭就走。喺我行到去B出口嗰邊個陣，個位巴打即刻追上前俾返錢我。<br />\n<br />\n雖然兩百蚊唔係好多，但都多謝你願意追返拎俾我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港其實好靚，香港人加油！</span></span>"},{"pid":"dea4bc0a6de56246b9e5ead60d4f372ef0adf9ab","tid":1289841,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"df20ac976c28098ef4904c78970895a0800b2eda","tid":1289841,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:24:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f0e2975f011b9c11570c071be114829617d5e02c","tid":1289841,"uid":179918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:24:06.000Z","msg":"真心  香港人其實係有良知同良心<br />\n係比啲大陸人溝撚淡左"},{"pid":"c4cbb5b1325524bf14bf1caffd447e850d34ddbb","tid":1289841,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5706871bb3ad1d03072eb91235e08c108f460cbb","tid":1289841,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67cead4bf6c3a7e177c670749465a50a67d7656a","tid":1289841,"uid":137628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:24:55.000Z","ms